= SDL_MaximizeWindow =

Make a window as large as possible.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void SDL_MaximizeWindow(SDL_Window *window);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''window'''
|the window to maximize
|}

== Version ==

This function is available since SDL 3.0.0.

